<div class = "container info-panel top-space">
    <b>Hi, there.</b>
    If you encounter any problems with the website please send an email to <b><a href = "mailto:contact@pmreferrals.ca">contact@pmreferrals.ca</a></b>,
    and I'll try to fix the issue as soon as possible.
</div>

<div class = "container" style = "margin-top: 5%">
    <div class = "row bottom-space">
        <div class = "three columns bottom-space">
            <img class = "u-max-full-width" src = "/images/sim.png"></img>
        </div>
        <div class = "nine columns">
            <h4>New to Public Mobile?</h4>
            <p>
                Get a randomized referral from an existing Public Mobile customer. Use it when activating your SIM card for a <b>$10 one-time credit.</b>
            </p>
            <a href = "/referral" class = "button confirm">Get a referral number</a>
            <br>
            <b>{{usage_count}}</b> referrals requested
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class = "row bottom-space">
        <div class = "three columns bottom-space">
            <img class = "u-max-full-width" src = "/images/bill.png"></img>
        </div>
        <div class = "nine columns">
            <h4>Existing Public Mobile customer?</h4>
            <p>
                Sign up to start collecting automatic referrals. Each successful referral takes <b>$1 off</b> your monthly bill.
                You'll also get a <b>custom referral code</b> so you can safely share your referral on public forums.
            </p>
            <a href = "/join" class = "right-space button active">Register your phone number</a>
            <a href = "/login" class = "button">View your PMReferrals.ca account</a>
            <br>
            <b>{{referral_count}}</b> registered users
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

